#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What does @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name do to prevent the argument from getting out of hand?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He draws their attention away from the problem, involves them in a positive activity, and gives them praise"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. He quickly intervenes to distract them, and gives a positive instruction to redirect them to a positive behaviour."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He reminds them it’s important to get along"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He gives them a warning for a consequence"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name gives the children a positive instruction to redirect them to a positive behaviour."
msgstr ""

